name: GAIN ゲイン 01
description: Acquisitio (Acquisition) is one of the auspicious figures of geomancy, an ancient earth divination system. It symbolizes success, profit and prosperity. Its astrological correspondence is Jupiter, a planet that brings good luck and material benefits, as well as Sagittarius and Taurus. It's good for meditation and attunement to the favorable resolution of various issues on the material plane, as well as enhancing good luck.
